Authenticity
We established one of the industry’s most robust programs to protect the integrity of the UGC on your site and sales channels.


Network reach
Our extensive data gives you visibility into your brand’s performance and the reach of your content across our massive network.


Human moderation
Advanced technology and nearly 300 highly trained human moderators protect your brand while screening for valuable insights.



Client services
We employ 160 in customer service to provided best-practice guidance and services, ensuring your success with Bazaarvoice.


Powerful insights
Monitor content performance, identify advocates, see sentiment trends, develop messaging, spot product opportunities. 


Global platform
Our solutions are deployed across the globe, positively impacting consumers and businesses in 37 languages.




